<PolicyPage
  title="Editorial Policy"
  description="The editorial standards behind Kixup News."
>
  <p>
    Kixup News prioritizes accuracy, clarity, and useful context. Articles should distinguish confirmed facts from interpretation and avoid overstating rumors or incomplete reporting.
  </p>
  <p>
    Explainers are written for readers who may be new to global soccer, so the site avoids unnecessary jargon and defines important terms when they appear.
  </p>
  <p>
    The site does not publish betting content, betting picks, or gambling promotions.
  </p>
</PolicyPage>
